column5: More info pinned at the top.  Judge and Jester 17 King St. E. Grimsby  Map to Judge & Jester  Hope to see you there!
I'd love to go and meet some of you guys, but I work 2-10pm today   . Maybe next time....have a good one!
I will be there, even if I have to drag a friend or two...  cheers,  Jen
Oh man, I was all set to go to this but was reminded that it was my youngest boy's birthday today. Have fun everyone.
Sorry to hear that you won't be there Pete.  Enjoy your day with Junior!
I'll see you there Roger - be leaving soon to head up. ( bump to top )

unfortunatly i wont be making it  recently found out my aunt has been diagnosed with cancer, a few small spots on her brain, and there is no telling how long she has.. so im pretty depressed.. i am sure you all will have a great time...  drink a few for me!....Bud
OK, who's swingin' by to pick me up???  I'm dressed and waiting!
